				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You can protect your computer pretty comprehensively from adverts and spyware  for free.
<br />

<br />
1) Virus scanner: <a href="http://www.grisoft.com/us/us_dwnl_free.php" target="_blank" class="postlink">AVG</a>
<br />
2) Firewall: <a href="http://www.zonelabs.com/store/content/company/products/znalm/freeDownload.jsp?lid=zadb_zadown" target="_blank" class="postlink">ZoneAlarm</a>
<br />
3) Ad/spyware removers: <a href="http://www.lavasoftusa.com/support/download/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Adaware</a> and <a href="http://www.safer-networking.org/index.php?lang=en&page=download" target="_blank" class="postlink">Spybot</a>
<br />
4) Pop-up blockers: <a href="http://www.panicware.com/product_psfree.html" target="_blank" class="postlink">Pop Up Stopper</a> for IE, <a href="http://www.mozilla.org/products/firebird/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Mozilla Firebird</a> has built in support<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=86775&resize=true" target="_new">Magelo</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
