				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The only drawback of the Google toolbar is that is nicely keeps track of what you have been watching on the net, just as it keeps track of your Google searches unless you disabled cookies.
<br />

<br />
Always make sure you have cookies disabled for search engines <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
It takes a bit of time to set up and now and then a check that everything is still all right with updates and such (although most can be automated), but the primary defense system of AVG and ZoneAlarm (prof version) as Eduano mentioned I have at home as well, and never had any trouble with viruses, popups, ads, spyware.
<br />

<br />

<br />
If you combine that with a good broadband router with integrated firewall you won't have much problems if you keep your software up to date.<br />_________________<br />Udaai Fateweaver - Battlemage
<br />
Eight Virtues
<br />
Venril Sathir
<br />
